Description: The functions in this package allow you to quickly create a shiny application for dose adaptation.
Depends: R (>= 3.5.0)
Imports: tdmore,dplyr, rjson, jsonlite, lubridate, mongolite, 
  shiny, shinyBS, tidyverse, plotly, shinyjs, DT,
  rhandsontable (<= 0.3.7), R6, ggplot2, purrr, tidyr, htmltools, tibble, rlang
Note: The dependency on rhandsontable is limited to version 0.3.7, because of a
  particular licensing issue. Rhandsontable depends on handsontable.js, which changed
  from an MIT license to a proprietary license in version 7.0.0. This proprietary license
  prohibits commercial use, and is therefore not compatible with GPL.
  We are only compatible with rhandsontable <= 0.3.7 to ensure the proprietary license will not 
  cause licensing problems down the road.
